@DATABASE "Barbarian (Psygnosis)"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Barbarian (Psygnosis)"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                           Barbarian - Psygnosis
                           =====================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51005,255)"}          51005,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50914,0)"}          50914,0
      OR
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(27680,0)"}          27680,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         I haven't tested this one as I don't have the
                         game :(

                         Rastan
@endnode
